{"type": "article", "id": 27416, "title": "Puma与潮牌Bape合作，以及，匡威推了奥特曼特别款｜浮华日报", "description": "我们为你挑选了今天最重要和最好看的时尚新闻。", "date": "2016-05-27T10:16:50Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 755, "name": "足球"}, {"id": 28233, "name": "男士鞋履"}, {"id": 14026, "name": "度假系列"}, {"id": 28234, "name": "加勒比海"}, {"id": 28235, "name": "管理层变动"}, {"id": 17102, "name": "波西米亚"}, {"id": 2355, "name": "眼镜"}, {"id": 35, "name": "复古"}, {"id": 26358, "name": "A Bathing Ape"}, {"id": 1231, "name": "PUMA"}, {"id": 27, "name": "Nike"}, {"id": 325, "name": "Fendi"}, {"id": 17963, "name": "Madewell"}, {"id": 28236, "name": "revolve"}, {"id": 4485, "name": "J. Crew"}, {"id": 1864, "name": "Tiffany"}, {"id": 5171, "name": "Canada Goose"}, {"id": 25410, "name": "PVH"}, {"id": 1066, "name": "Calvin Klein"}], "category": 19, "column": 8, "author": 113313, "comment_count": 13, "praise_count": 106, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702143919sODGALz2ifyK7tSZ.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<h2>一些重要的新闻：</h2>\n<p><a href=\"http://wwd.com/retail-news/specialty-stores/j-crew-loss-sales-fall-10437867/\"><b>J. Crew 亏损收窄，销售额仍在下跌</b></a>｜J. Crew 宣布一季度净亏损收窄至 800 万美元，与去年同期 4.624 亿美元相比有大幅度的减少。息税折旧摊销前利润（EBITDA）与去年一季度的 4480 万美元相比有所增长，达到 4540 万美元。总收入从 5.818 亿下跌了 3% 至 5.675 亿美元。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://wwd.com/retail-news/designer-luxury/canada-goose-stores-new-york-toronto-10437687/\"><b>Canada Goose 将在纽约和多伦多开新店</b></a>｜加拿大奢侈外衣品牌 Canada Goose 宣布将于秋季在纽约 SoHo 区及多伦多 Yorkdale 购物中心开两家新门店，去年秋 Canada Goose 将品牌的线上购买平台拓展至美国，CEO 兼总裁 Dani Reiss 表示“取得了巨大成功”，并透露品牌在过去五年中收入达到 450% 的增长。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://wwd.com/business-news/financial/pvh-sales-earnings-calvin-klein-tommy-hilfiger-10437958/\"><b>PVH 一季度销售增长</b></a>｜PVH 集团截止 5 月 1 日的一季度内，净收益从 1.141 亿美元增长至 2.316 亿美元，净销售额从 17.8 亿涨至 18.1 亿美元，但仍略逊于 19 亿美元的预期。旗下 Calvin Klein  品牌收益增长了 13%，Tommy Hilfiger 则增长了 4%。</p>\n<p class=\"\"><a href=\"http://us.fashionmag.com/news/Nike-makes-general-management-changes-for-global-business,697129.html#.V0eSr4QrJQY\"><b>Nike 综合管理层变动</b></a>｜Nike 近日宣布 5 位综合管理层职位变动，在 Nike 任职 19 年的 Phil McCartney ，6 月 1 日起担任鞋履部门总经理兼副总裁。现任新兴市场总经理兼副总裁的 Tom Peddie 将于 7 月 1 日起担任北美综合市场总经理兼副总裁。Ann Hebert 则接替 Peddie 的职位。土耳其市场总经理 Christophe Merkel 将从 7 月 1 日起担任日本市场总经理。现任日本市场总经理 Jim Reynolds 则将担任运动专业部门总经理兼总裁。</p>\n<h2>一些值得一看的：</h2>\n<p class=\"\"><a href=\"http://www.fashiongonerogue.com/madewell-vacation-outfits-june-2016/\">Madewell 发布六月穿搭指南</a>，复古风格，看起来也很舒适：<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<p></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702143859XJv37CBglh1xPdTD.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.73214286\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702143859b0rKwPaldJIvXGRp.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.73148148\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702143900kYdP5nLOsSJmWB4v.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.73148148\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021439001F5ghpXPZ49YUkxy.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.73148148\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702143901YfiDJr16LIQ7h8tg.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.73148148\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\"><a href=\"http://www.vogue.com/fashion-shows/resort-2017/fendi/slideshow/collection#22\">Fendi 推出 2017 度假系列</a>：</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<p></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702143902EGr7OlCKw5mqcg4x.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75185185\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021439025N0XVzxSfIKDm1kg.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75185185\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702143903lpAmjf80BiPsJknG.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75185185\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702143903AI6jx1nhp9fTPGv4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75185185\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702143904Th2HZYsXOkJWNEM0.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.73703704\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702143905aLkNscrEQ5qiICbw.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75185185\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<p></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702143906W35CUyDqBVHQ8mFY.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.73703704\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\">Puma 与日本潮流品牌 A Bathing Ape 再次合作，<a href=\"http://www.freshnessmag.com/2016/05/25/puma-bape-spring-summer-2016-collection/\">推出足球主题系列</a>，包括 T 恤及跑鞋，并找来著名意大利足球球星 Mario Balotelli 拍摄 lookbook。5 月 28 日上市：</p>\n<p class=\"multiple\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702143906eGY9nKkXFNP7WMjm.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021439076dVrtgm7OhURHb1P.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702143907D6wkg5LapUB1Tzdi.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.76285714\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702143908x1wuL7Oc9Blq4pJP.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6675\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702143908tpQCJFHb0ki1mwTD.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p>\n<p class=\"\"><span style=\"text-align: left;\">度假的行头？可以看看</span><a href=\"http://www.fashiongonerogue.com/revolve-vacation-outfits-2016-shop/\" style=\"text-align: left;\"> REVOLVE 最新的“加勒比海丽人”</a><span style=\"text-align: left;\">系列：</span></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<p><span style=\"text-align: left;\"></span></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2016070214390990yxMClrwvNOdXZ8.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75277778\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702143909cFB6TS8y3NiqhKMO.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75277778\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702143910e3d0kYa5ZOjgArXh.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75277778\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\"><a href=\"http://www.highsnobiety.com/2016/05/26/balenciaga-fall-2016-footwear-collection/#slide-3\"> Balenciaga 2016 秋季男士鞋履系列</a>：<span style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br></span></p>\n<p class=\"multiple\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702143910zWYxdG4KOk0HCNfT.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702143911EJKTB7wDZ3RSteYn.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702143911RSEzbQc9XDVAp2LU.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021439122byJOnUk9fV7ZIts.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p>\n<p class=\"\"><span style=\"text-align: justify;\"></span></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702143912gsYq7aOHSTm9E5CZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p>\n<p class=\"\">蒙特利尔的眼镜品牌<a href=\"http://hypebeast.com/2016/5/all-in-eyewear-2016-spring-summer-lookbook\"> all in eyewear 推出了 90 年代复古感的新款 lookbook</a>：<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<p></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702143913eZcySw7Jarj9043O.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75498008\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702143913PG6aAyn1B8lmL3jH.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75498008\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702143914EDLJfbiWUR406AOF.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75498008\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p>为庆祝“奥特曼”（Ultraman）形象问世 50 周年， <a href=\"http://popbee.com/accessories/shoes/converse-x-ultraman-collaboration-sneakers/#\">Converse 推出联名纪念鞋款</a>：<br></p>\n<p class=\"multiple\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702143914HAvlgPUI7JY6rE2f.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702143915yZ1Jz932dTehrLio.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702143916si0cWSr8n2DVwuOF.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702143916SmnRFMA9Ygk7LqrZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702143917P4qj1bp8tTABgdIX.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2016070214391774X691ZtUK3dMOwP.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p>\n<p class=\"\"><br></p>\n\n"}